ightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4800x2700+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc5%2F22%2F7a2ea9494f96a50a8939b5fde473%2Fweek1-b-digital-main-art-16x9.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4800x2700+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc5%2F22%2F7a2ea9494f96a50a8939b5fde473%2Fweek1-b-digital-main-art-16x9.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4800x2700+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc5%2F22%2F7a2ea9494f96a50a8939b5fde473%2Fweek1-b-digital-main-art-16x9.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4800x2700+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc5%2F22%2F7a2ea9494f96a50a8939b5fde473%2Fweek1-b-digital-main-art-16x9.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4800x2700+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc5%2F22%2F7a2ea9494f96a50a8939b5fde473%2Fweek1-b-digital-main-art-16x9.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4800x2700+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc5%2F22%2F7a2ea9494f96a50a8939b5fde473%2Fweek1-b-digital-main-art-16x9.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/4800x2700+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fc5%2F22%2F7a2ea9494f96a50a8939b5fde473%2Fweek1-b-digital-main-art-16x9.jpg" class="img" alt="week1_b_digital_main_art_16x9.jpg" loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Stress Less is a new series from NPR that will help you find your calm. Subscribe to &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/newsletter/stress-less"&gt;&lt;em&gt;the Stress Less newsletter series&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; for more powerful tools and strategies to help reduce anxiety and improve feelings of well-being.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stress can't be eliminated, but it can be managed better and sometimes even turned into a force for good by changing how you think about it.&lt;/strong&gt; Psychologist Jeremy Jamieson says that the stress response, like an increased heart rate, can give us the energy we need to handle the demands we face. Explaining the benefits of stress responses can also help people embrace stress as a response. But it’s &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/10/18/nx-s1-5115911/stress-manage-anxiety-health-help"&gt;important to manage stress because&lt;/a&gt; it can persist during times when they are not needed and cause further problems.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-28889" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 6558;         --source-height: 3687;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/1800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/6558x3687+0+685/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F50%2Faa%2F4b6cfcff450e920e1cdd1d643528%2Fgettyimages-2076703127.jpg" class="img" alt="A golden retriever races through the snow during a storm on March 14 in Boulder, Colorado." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 A golden retriever races through the snow during a storm on March 14 in Boulder, Colorado.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Mark Makela/Getty Images                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The NOAA's Climate Prediction Center's winter outlook report &lt;/strong&gt;details that a La Niña event has a 60% chance of emerging by the end of November. Here’s &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/10/18/nx-s1-5157206/noaa-winter-weather-outlook-2024-2025"&gt;a map showing how your state&lt;/a&gt; will be affected.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Treehouse Foods, known for producing brands like Kodiak Cakes, Simple Truth and Foodhold&lt;/strong&gt;, is &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/10/19/nx-s1-5158372/frozen-waffles-recall-listeria"&gt;recalling frozen waffles&lt;/a&gt; sold at major supermarket chains due to listeria contamination concerns. The recall is related to products sold in the U.S. and in Canada.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Biden administration is proposing a rule that would provide women with private insurance access&lt;/strong&gt; to over-the-counter birth control pills and other &lt;a href="http://www.npr.org/2024/10/20/g-s1-29117/over-the-counter-birth-control-condoms-free"&gt;contraceptives at no cost&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/1155154221/majd-al-waheidi"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Majd Al-Waheidi&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
