/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/png" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/png/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1294x728+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Faa%2F75%2F4fc7edb44f06a99a70f824ce8938%2Fscreenshot-2024-10-16-at-5-39-20-am.png" class="img" alt="Screenshot 2024-10-16 at 5.39.20 AM.png" loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Stress Less is a new series from NPR that will help you find your calm. Subscribe to the &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/newsletter/stress-less"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;u&gt;Stress Less newsletter series&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt; for more powerful tools and strategies to help reduce anxiety and improve feelings of well-being.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Around one in four people in the U.S. say they’ve ended a friendship due to political disagreements&lt;/strong&gt;, according to a recent survey. With the divisive election just mere weeks away, it can be hard to talk about politics. Studies show that polarization can lead to isolation, stress, and anger. There are &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/10/14/nx-s1-5057929/anxiety-stress-politics-election-2024-polarization"&gt;some strategies to reduce election stress&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;ul class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;🤝 &lt;strong&gt;Braver Angels, a group aiming to help Americans bridge the political divide, says&lt;/strong&gt; stereotyping, dismissing, ridiculing and contempt create polarization.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;🤝 &lt;strong&gt;Polarization can be countered by asking yourself a series of questions, including: &lt;/strong&gt;Are you judging people as “worthless” or “deplorable” and not seeing them as fully human?&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;🤝 &lt;strong&gt;Once you understand your own attitudes clearly, the next step is &lt;/strong&gt;to reconsider the story you tell yourself about people with opposing views.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;🤝 &lt;strong&gt;Seek out news showcasing different points of view. &lt;/strong&gt;When we tune into the same media outlets, we are likely exposing ourselves to only a small portion of information.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;       &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here is &lt;/strong&gt;the full list of &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/10/14/nx-s1-5057929/anxiety-stress-politics-election-2024-polarization"&gt;tips to help bridge the divide&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;3 things to know before you go&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-28280" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 5943;         --source-height: 3343;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/webp" /&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5943x3343+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F28%2F87%2Fec51188c43b986086f252d232048%2Fwalgreens-sign.jpg" class="img" alt="Walgreens will close 1,200 stores, the company announced Tuesday. Here, a sign is posted in front of a Walgreens store on March 09, 2023 in El Cerrito, California." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Walgreens will close 1,200 stores over three years, the company announced on Tuesday.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Justin Sullivan/Getty Images                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Walgreens announced yesterday that it plans to close 1,200 stores &lt;/strong&gt;over three years to aid its turnaround efforts. The company is &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/10/15/nx-s1-5153532/walgreens-closing-1200-stores"&gt;grappling with retail competition&lt;/a&gt; and lower prescription payouts.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;German airline Lufthansa has agreed to pay a $4 million penalty&lt;/strong&gt;, the U.S. Department of Transportation announced yesterday. The airline is &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2024/10/15/nx-s1-5153909/lufthansa-jewish-discrimination-record-penalty"&gt;facing allegations of discrimination&lt;/a&gt; against Jewish passengers during an incident in May 2022.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mark Robinson, the Republican candidate for governor in North Carolina, has filed a defamation lawsuit&lt;/strong&gt; against CNN and a former porn store employee over &lt;a href="https://www.wunc.org/politics/2024-10-15/mark-robinson-lawsuit-cnn-porn-store-2024-election-binnall"&gt;reports of inappropriate behavior online&lt;/a&gt;. (via &lt;a href="https://www.wunc.org/"&gt;WUNC&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/859721331/suzanne-nuyen"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Suzanne Nuyen&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
